formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: At the time of registration the work of tower A and B was completed 100%. The architect certificate at the time of registration also has the same status. The purpose of registration was the development and sale of Tower C for which we had a approved plan. But after the registration, TP was declared and the road was put in the land where tower C was to be built. Considering this the development of Tower C was not possible. And we have applied for the removing Tower C in the alteration. All the flats of A and B were booked and  money has been received from the Allottees way in 2018. Few of the flat owners kept the money outstanding the receipt of which was reported in Quarter-5 as Quarter 2 to 4 was locked due to non compliance. After that nothing is been received.
